Package nl.naturalis.geneious.util

Utility classes.
Author:
Ayco Holleman
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CharsetDetector
    Utility class to guess the encoding of a given byte buffer.
    DocumentLookupTable<K>
    Caches documents, either selected by the user or retrieved through a database query, in a HashMap for fast lookups as an importer iterates over the rows in a CSV or file or spreadsheet.
    DocumentUtils
    Various methods related to Geneious documents.
    JsonUtil
    Provides method for serializing objects to JSON.
    Messages
    Common messages or messages so verbose that they would clutter the code that emits them too much.
    Messages.Debug
    Common DEBUG messages.
    Messages.Error
    Common ERROR messages.
    Messages.Info
    Common INFO messages.
    Messages.Warn
    Common WARN messages.
    NaturalisIcons
    Provides differently sized and differently colored Naturalis icons.
    Ping
    Pings the database to ascertain that all documents have been indexed.
    PingHistory
    Generates and saves unique ping values that are inserted as extract IDs into special, temporary documents.
    PingSequence
    An extension of DefaultNucleotideSequence solely meant to create "ping documents".
    PreconditionValidator
    Checks whether all preconditions for executing an operation are met and, if not, throws an PreconditionException.
    QueryUtils
    Methods for querying the Geneious database.
    StoredDocumentComparator
    Sorts StoredDocument instances according to the document version (descending).
